{"tid":2184382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾多次指香港奉行三權分立　陳弘毅：是否用三權分立詞語　背後原則不變","createTime":"2020-09-01T13:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T14:44:21.000Z","uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6754e552849dc354851b87b9c48b2c25976020e6","tid":2184382,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9B%BE%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%8C%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%89%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%86%E7%AB%8B-%E9%99%B3%E5%BC%98%E6%AF%85-%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%86%E7%AB%8B%E8%A9%9E%E8%AA%9E-%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A/#.X05DFVuM5_E.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%2589%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BC%2598%25E6%25AF%2585-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25A9%259E%25E8%25AA%259E-%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AE%258A%2F%23.X05DFVuM5_E.facebook&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=5f75cbad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%2589%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BC%2598%25E6%25AF%2585-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25A9%259E%25E8%25AA%259E-%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AE%258A%2F%23.X05DFVuM5_E.facebook&h=419a9091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9B%BE%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%8C%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%89%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%86%E7%AB%8B-%E9%99%B3%E5%BC%98%E6%AF%85-%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%86%E7%AB%8B%E8%A9%9E%E8%AA%9E-%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A/#.X05DFVuM5_E.facebook</a><br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日表示支持教育局局長楊潤雄言論，重申「香港確實沒有三權分立」，立法會議員郭榮鏗批評說法可笑及不尊重司法機關，又指基本法委員會委員、港大法律學者陳弘毅過去亦有引用「三權分立」的原則。陳弘毅回應《立場》查詢時，沒有正面回應香港是否存在三權分立，又表示「separation of power」不一定指三權分立，現時只是政治體制描述上的爭拗，不是具體的法律爭議。<br />\n<br />\n陳弘毅在 2016 年接受有線電視專訪，強調香港是奉行三權分立，他去年在《明報》刊登的文章《誰來監督警察？》，亦提及「在奉行三權分立的現代法治社會裏，我們有立法、司法和行政機關」。今日被問及香港是否存在三權分立的制度，陳弘毅無直接回應，他說無論是否用此詞語，其背後的原則亦是行政和立法是互相配合而由互相制衡，司法則為獨立。<br />\n<br />\n至於運用三權分立一詞形容香港制度是否準確，陳弘毅只就英語用詞作回應，指過去有案例判決時採用「separation of power （分權）」一詞，又指有人認為「separation of power」不一定指三權分立，但無進一步解釋。他認為有關三權分立的討論只是政治體系描述上的問題，並非具體法律爭議，日後法院繼續採用「separation of power」一詞是沒有問題。"},{"pid":"f3642d8e7b2053cb4e5eb28c8053855f7eebfc2a","tid":2184382,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"十二位手足被扣押第九日 務必繼續關注聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184284</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"064a2f56390eb16069117bbf68fc403b91e0c380","tid":2184382,"uid":85235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"即刻諗返起個時玩語言藝術話反送中壽終正寢<br />\n而家唔承認三權分立就不斷搬啲詞語出嚟扮冇事"},{"pid":"30b2a4fbbb8a8f4742cc9e8712abb99456502165","tid":2184382,"uid":23672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"條友以前明明好地地 做乜呢一年搞到成個十一哥咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1fa544bf6570df9d4209be03793c029cb73503","tid":2184382,"uid":49609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"係就係，唔係就唔係，你都on9"},{"pid":"3d0394e3c262d02ba11c77e615a94c8e8d282eed","tid":2184382,"uid":54623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply